data.title: SocalPresa King Cali & Nina (N3) Litter 3 - Perro de Presa Canario Puppies for Sale
data.meta_description: Meet the litter 2 of SocalPresa King Cali & Nina N2 Perro de Presa Canario puppies for sale. Explore their lineage and availability. Visit us
data.meta_site_name: SoCalPresa: Top-Rated Presa Canario Puppies for Sale
data.text:
We are pleased to announce our litter of SocalPresa King Cali and SocalPresa Nina Litter 3!

Litter will be expecting to arrive October the 27th of 2017, and will be available for permanent homes right before Christmas!

We will be expecting mostly Black Brindle Presa Canario Puppies just like her first litter with King Cali.

You can reserve a puppy by clicking this link, or visiting the Presa Canario Puppy Reserve link above.

Nina is a great mother who has produced 2 previous litters, one being the now famous tittle of “SocalPresa Tyson” which is 28 inches at the withers, and built like a semi truck!

We strive to keep the authentic Presa Canario genes with extremely low health issues in order to breed the highest Perro de Presa Canario puppy possible.

All our puppies are contracted only to good families, and have a guarantee on their health.

Stud: SocalPresa King | Height: 30″ Withers | Weight: 158lbs. | Color: Brindle

SocalPresa King Cali is a powerful Presa Canario that could easily be an amazing hunter as he is massive and an agile beast. He has an excellent bond with family, and is playful, but fearsome to strangers and intruders. Perfect health, raw power, bear like size and extreme intelligence make him a very desired Presa Canario stud. Easy to leave home unattended when you have a “King” to your disposal. This type of dog might be something you and your family might be longing for.
